extends layout 

block content 
  p This will erase the Inventory database and replenish it with default data.
  p Please enter the admin passcode to continue with the reset.
  form(method='POST' action='') 
    label(
      for='passcode'
    ) Passcode:  
    input#passcode(
      type='text'
      required='true'
      name='passcode'
    )
    button(
      type='submit'
    ) Reset
  if wrongCode 
    p Incorrect passcode provided, please try again.